Features an easy grip handle, zipper closure along with mesh inspection panels for easy identification of contents. Compact stove is high quality aluminum alloy and stainless steel. Camp stove is durable, with an adjustable flame control that allows excellent cooking versatility. The wind shield increases efficiency in breezy condition. Compatible with most screw type camping gas/propane canisters (not included). Boils 1 liter of water in under 3.5 minutes.  Weigh just 3.17 ounces and pack dimensions are 4.5x2x2. Camp-A-Box comes complete with plate with lid and bowl, small and large Fold-A-Cup, cutting board, spork, and 3 compartment spice shaker. Replacement filter uses advanced technology that removes what most other filters cannot. The Survival Camp Set includes: Pakbox 4, Camp-A-Box complete, Fliptop advanced filtration water bottl is made from BPA free plastic.  Filter life up to 100 gallons or more, depending upon the quality of the source water. Removes up to 99.99% of Virus, Bacteria, and E-Coli. Also removes up to 99.99% of Chromium 6, Chlorine, Lead, Mercury, Cadium, Aluminum, and Copper. Removes up to 99.9% of Micro-organisms, such as Giardia, and Cryptosporidium. Not for use with salt water.  Weight is 6.4 ounces.  Advanced replacement filter, Lightweight compact stove, and an Outdoor survival guide.Snugpak Survival 5 Piece Camp Set in Carrying Case- Olive

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
